---
title: Smoky Bean Loaded Wedges with Avocado and Cheese
description: Load up on flavour with our Smoky Bean Loaded Wedges for a delicious veggie dinner. Hot sauce plus our roasted spice and herb blend gives these beans a smoky and punchy taste that make these wedges worth waiting for.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R42_W40_UK_V16733-6_Main_low_2-2bd2eecb.jpg
